rows.label: qst201204_0010
rows.name: Erm... Are these your children, by any chance?

rows.label: qst201204_0020
rows.name: Yeah, so?

rows.label: qst201204_0030
rows.name:
What's it to you?
Have they got 'emselves into trouble again, or wh-

rows.label: qst201204_0040
rows.name: T-t-two Blades with eyepatches?!

rows.label: qst201204_0050
rows.name:
What do you think you're doing with my boys?!
Go away, now!

rows.label: qst201204_0060
rows.name:
Is he OK?
Doesn't seem too open to a chin-wag here...

rows.label: qst201204_0070
rows.name:
Mikumari...
Maybe we should leave now...?

rows.label: qst201204_0080
rows.name:
No! It's fine!
All I wanted to do was have a little talk!

rows.label: qst201204_0090
rows.name:
Look... Please, hear me out.
All we want to do is apologize for the past.

rows.label: qst201204_0100
rows.name:
Someone, please!
Somebody come help!

rows.label: qst201204_0110
rows.name: They're gonna kill my lads!

rows.label: qst201204_0120
rows.name:
Wait!
Nobody's here to harm you!

rows.label: qst201204_0130
rows.name:
Don't come any closer, you monster!
And don't lay a finger on my kids!

rows.label: qst201204_0140
rows.name:
Look, just calm down.
Shut up, or I'll shut you up.

rows.label: qst201204_0150
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Scared noise

rows.label: qst201204_0160
rows.name:
Seori... Give it a rest!
You're scaring the man!

rows.label: qst201204_0170
rows.name: But...

rows.label: qst201204_0180
rows.name: It's OK. I'll handle it.

rows.label: qst201204_0190
rows.name:
Listen will you? We're not here to hurt you
any more than we already... Ugh.

rows.label: qst201204_0200
rows.name:
You! Blades!
Don't move a muscle!

rows.label: qst201204_0210
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?!

rows.label: qst201204_0220
rows.name:
This looks like an unsavory situation.
Rex?

rows.label: qst201204_0230
rows.name: I can see that...

rows.label: qst201204_0240
rows.name:
Th-thank you!
Quick now! Get those Blades!

rows.label: qst201204_0250
rows.name:
That's them all right!
It's those Core Crystal hunters!

rows.label: qst201204_0260
rows.name: Just waltzing in here, in broad daylight!

rows.label: qst201204_0270
rows.name:
Hey! Not so fast!
We aren't the bad dudes!

rows.label: qst201204_0280
rows.name: Another one-eyer!

rows.label: qst201204_0290
rows.name: Didn't realize there were three of 'em!

rows.label: qst201204_0300
rows.name: Whoa! I'm not...

rows.label: qst201204_0310
rows.name: All we wanted to do was talk to this man!

rows.label: qst201204_0320
rows.name: Quiet, bandit trash!

rows.label: qst201204_0330
rows.name: Well said!

rows.label: qst201204_0340
rows.name:
Grab the lot of 'em!
We'll get a nice bounty if we bring 'em in!

rows.label: qst201204_0350
rows.name:
Well, Mikumari? What do you think?
Are we going to fight these losers?

rows.label: qst201204_0360
rows.name: But...

rows.label: qst201204_0370
rows.name:
Mikumari! Seori!
I think you'd better give up on the idea of a nice chat.

rows.label: qst201204_0380
rows.name:
It's unfortunate... But I'm afraid
they'll need our help calming down.

rows.label: qst201204_0390
rows.name: You two, happy to help, yeah?

rows.label: qst201204_0400
rows.name: Sure! Not a problem!

rows.label: qst201204_0410
rows.name:
You OK with that, Seori?
Don't kill, just incapacitate.

rows.label: qst201204_0420
rows.name:
This is an opportunity to show them
we've really changed.

rows.label: qst201204_0430
rows.name: Yes... Will do.
